title: Overview of the Tumi Voyageur Capri Crossbody Bag
description:
Buy Now - http://abt.com/search/search.php?keywords=tumi+voyageur+crossbody+capri
Shop Tumi - http://abt.com/brand/Tumi

The best-selling Voyageur collection offers streamlined and sophisticated feminine styling with smart details in lightweight designs. Perfect for travel or everyday use, this slim crossbody design offers an extra sense of security. Features include interior and exterior pockets and top zip closure. Strap adjusts to maximum length of 51".

• External Features:
o Front zip pocket
o Back open pocket
o Adjustable shoulder strap
o Detachable tag with mirror
• Internal Features:
o Zip pocket
o Open pocket
o Media pocket
o Pen loops
